Utility for automatically flip the screen when the monitor is rotated to the vertical position and back to the horizontal position. 

It uses serial port. 
When Rxd and Txd are connected screen flips to the veritcal position, when aren't connected flips to the horizontal.

OS:
	Linux

Run:
	1. make
	2. sudo ./flip_screen /dev/ttyS0 (for example)

Read:
	http://habrahabr.ru/post/137650/
